    <item>
      <title>由于金属价格暴跌，Sibanye 遭受 25 亿美元减值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sibanye-takes-2-5-billion-impairment-after-metal-prices-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sibanye Stillwater Ltd. 预计去年将出现亏损，原因是铂族金属价格暴跌以及其各业务的运营问题迫使其计提了 475 亿兰特（25 亿美元）的减值准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sibanye-takes-2-5-billion-impairment-after-metal-prices-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称斯里兰卡将向债券持有人提供新的重组计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sri-lanka-said-to-offer-new-restructruring-plan-to-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，斯里兰卡通过其顾问拉扎德向美元债券持有人发出了一份新的重组提案，因为这个南亚国家寻求彻底整顿其违约债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sri-lanka-said-to-offer-new-restructruring-plan-to-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 05:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗奇表示，除非中国解决自己的经济问题，否则香港就完了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/hong-kong-is-over-unless-china-fixes-its-own-economy-roach-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利亚洲有限公司前董事长史蒂芬·罗奇(Stephen Roach)在撰写的一篇悲观专栏引发轩然大波后表示，如果中国希望这个金融中心拥有更好的未来，就必须修复经济并让香港自治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/hong-kong-is-over-unless-china-fixes-its-own-economy-roach-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 02:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股指期货在美联储会议纪要之前下跌，英伟达：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待上次美联储政策会议纪要以及英伟达公司的财报，美国股指期货下跌。高盛集团称“地球上最重要的股票”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 22:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
